definitionFileDescription:
path to a browserforce definition file
The schema is similar to the scratch org definition file.
See https://github.com/amtrack/sfdx-browserforce-plugin#supported-org-preferences for supported values.
planFileDescription: path to a browserforce plan file
stateFileDescription: path to a browserforce state file
applyCommandDescription: apply a plan from a plan file or remote state
planCommandDescription: retrieve state and generate plan file
